---
// About.astro
---
<section class="about fade px-[20px] py-[50px] md:px-[60px] md:py-[100px]" id="about">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h2 data-es="Sobre mí" data-en="About Me">Sobre mí</h2>
        <div class="header-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-[30px] md:gap-[80px] items-center">
        <div class="about-text">
            <p class="mb-[30px] text-[1.1rem]" data-es="Desarrollador web con base en Granada. El frontend es mi fuerte — HTML, CSS y JS — pero también trabajo con datos: Supabase, SQL y Looker Studio para convertir bases de datos en estudios de mercado y dashboards accionables. Si algo se puede automatizar con n8n, se automatiza." data-en="Web developer based in Granada. Frontend is my strength — HTML, CSS and JS — but I also work with data: Supabase, SQL and Looker Studio to turn databases into market studies and actionable dashboards. If something can be automated with n8n, it gets automated.">
                Desarrollador web con base en Granada. El frontend es mi fuerte — HTML, CSS y JS — pero también trabajo con datos: Supabase, SQL y Looker Studio para convertir bases de datos en estudios de mercado y dashboards accionables.
            </p>
            <ul class="about-highlights list-none grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-[20px] p-0 m-0">
                <li data-es="✦ Frontend · HTML · CSS · JavaScript" data-en="✦ Frontend · HTML · CSS · JavaScript">✦ Frontend · HTML · CSS · JavaScript</li>
                <li data-es="✦ SQL · Supabase · Looker Studio" data-en="✦ SQL · Supabase · Looker Studio">✦ SQL · Supabase · Looker Studio</li>
                <li data-es="✦ Automatización · n8n · REST API" data-en="✦ Automation · n8n · REST API">✦ Automatización · n8n · REST API</li>
                <li data-es="✦ PHP · MySQL · Accesibilidad · UX" data-en="✦ PHP · MySQL · Accessibility · UX">✦ PHP · MySQL · Accesibilidad · UX</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-[30px]">
            <div class="stat-card-about bg-bg-light border border-slate-400/10 p-[40px] rounded-[16px] text-center transition-all duration-300 cursor-default hover:border-accent-cyan hover:bg-accent-cyan/5 hover:translate-y-[-5px] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)]">
                <h3 class="counter text-[3rem] bg-linear-to-br from-accent-cyan to-[#8b5cf6] text-transparent bg-clip-text mb-[10px]" data-target="5">0</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-[1rem] m-0" data-es="Proyectos Completados" data-en="Completed Projects">Proyectos Completados</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card-about bg-bg-light border border-slate-400/10 p-[40px] rounded-[16px] text-center transition-all duration-300 cursor-default hover:border-accent-cyan hover:bg-accent-cyan/5 hover:translate-y-[-5px] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)]">
                <h3 class="counter text-[3rem] bg-linear-to-br from-accent-cyan to-[#8b5cf6] text-transparent bg-clip-text mb-[10px]" data-target="2">0</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-[1rem] m-0" data-es="Años de Experiencia" data-en="Years of Experience">Años de Experiencia</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card-about bg-bg-light border border-slate-400/10 p-[40px] rounded-[16px] text-center transition-all duration-300 cursor-default hover:border-accent-cyan hover:bg-accent-cyan/5 hover:translate-y-[-5px] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)]">
                <h3 class="text-[3rem] bg-linear-to-br from-accent-cyan to-[#8b5cf6] text-transparent bg-clip-text mb-[10px]">100%</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-[1rem] m-0" data-es="Dedicación" data-en="Dedication">Dedicación</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>



<!-- HOBBIES SECTION -->
<div class="hobbies-section max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-[20px] md:px-[60px] overflow-hidden max-h-0 opacity-0 transition-all duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)] relative z-2 [&.open]:max-h-[1400px] lg:[&.open]:max-h-[900px] [&.open]:opacity-100 [&.open]:pb-[60px] md:[&.open]:pb-[80px]" id="hobbies-section">
    <div class="hobbies-header text-center mb-[50px] pt-[20px]">
        <h2 class="text-[2.2rem] mb-[10px]" data-es="Más allá del código" data-en="Beyond the Code">Más allá del código</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-[0.95rem]" data-es="Porque un desarrollador también tiene vida fuera de la pantalla." data-en="Because a developer also has a life outside the screen.">Porque un desarrollador también tiene vida fuera de la pantalla.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hobbies-grid grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-[24px]">
        <div class="hobby-card bg-bg-light border border-white/10 rounded-[16px] py-[32px] px-[24px] text-center transition-all duration-300 cursor-default relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-accent-cyan/50 hover:translate-y-[-5px] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)] before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:w-full before:h-[2px] before:bg-linear-to-r before:from-accent-cyan before:to-[#8b5cf6] before:opacity-0 before:transition-opacity before:duration-300 hover:before:opacity-100">
            <span class="hobby-emoji text-[3rem] block mb-[15px] transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]">⚽</span>
            <h3 class="text-[1.2rem] mb-[10px] text-white" data-es="Árbitro de Fútbol" data-en="Football Referee">Árbitro de Fútbol</h3>
            <p class="text-[0.9rem] text-slate-400 m-0 leading-[1.6]" data-es="Árbitro federado. En el campo aprendo que las normas existen para garantizar la justicia — igual que en el código limpio." data-en="Certified referee. On the pitch I learn that rules exist to ensure fairness — just like in clean code.">Árbitro federado. En el campo aprendo que las normas existen para garantizar la justicia — igual que en el código limpio.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hobby-card bg-bg-light border border-white/10 rounded-[16px] py-[32px] px-[24px] text-center transition-all duration-300 cursor-default relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-accent-cyan/50 hover:translate-y-[-5px] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)] before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:w-full before:h-[2px] before:bg-linear-to-r before:from-accent-cyan before:to-[#8b5cf6] before:opacity-0 before:transition-opacity before:duration-300 hover:before:opacity-100">
            <span class="hobby-emoji text-[3rem] block mb-[15px] transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]">🏃‍♂️</span>
            <h3 class="text-[1.2rem] mb-[10px] text-white" data-es="Apasionado del Deporte" data-en="Sports Enthusiast">Apasionado del Deporte</h3>
            <p class="text-[0.9rem] text-slate-400 m-0 leading-[1.6]" data-es="El deporte forma parte de mi rutina diaria. Disciplina, constancia y esfuerzo: valores que aplico también al desarrollo." data-en="Sport is part of my daily routine. Discipline, consistency and effort: values I also apply to development.">El deporte forma parte de mi rutina diaria. Disciplina, constancia y esfuerzo: valores que aplico también al desarrollo.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hobby-card bg-bg-light border border-white/10 rounded-[16px] py-[32px] px-[24px] text-center transition-all duration-300 cursor-default relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-accent-cyan/50 hover:translate-y-[-5px] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)] before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:w-full before:h-[2px] before:bg-linear-to-r before:from-accent-cyan before:to-[#8b5cf6] before:opacity-0 before:transition-opacity before:duration-300 hover:before:opacity-100">
            <span class="hobby-emoji text-[3rem] block mb-[15px] transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]">🚵</span>
            <h3 class="text-[1.2rem] mb-[10px] text-white" data-es="Mountain Bike" data-en="Mountain Bike">Mountain Bike</h3>
            <p class="text-[0.9rem] text-slate-400 m-0 leading-[1.6]" data-es="Durante muchos años recorrí rutas y senderos de montaña. La naturaleza te da perspectiva que ninguna pantalla puede ofrecer." data-en="For many years I rode mountain trails and routes. Nature gives you perspective that no screen can offer.">Durante muchos años recorrí rutas y senderos de montaña. La naturaleza te da perspectiva que ninguna pantalla puede ofrecer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hobby-card bg-bg-light border border-white/10 rounded-[16px] py-[32px] px-[24px] text-center transition-all duration-300 cursor-default relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-accent-cyan/50 hover:translate-y-[-5px] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)] before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:w-full before:h-[2px] before:bg-linear-to-r before:from-accent-cyan before:to-[#8b5cf6] before:opacity-0 before:transition-opacity before:duration-300 hover:before:opacity-100">
            <span class="hobby-emoji text-[3rem] block mb-[15px] transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]">🐾</span>
            <h3 class="text-[1.2rem] mb-[10px] text-white" data-es="Amante de los Animales" data-en="Animal Lover">Amante de los Animales</h3>
            <p class="text-[0.9rem] text-slate-400 m-0 leading-[1.6]" data-es="Los animales son leales, honestos y nunca te fallan. Cualidades que también busco en el código que escribo." data-en="Animals are loyal, honest and never fail you. Qualities I also look for in the code I write.">Los animales son leales, honestos y nunca te fallan. Cualidades que también busco en el código que escribo.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
